freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Chilblain in bilateral 4th and 5th fingers acting up. Very itchy, red and swollen
Episodes of blurry vision both eyes

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Eye photosensitivity to lights when i woke up this am, had wavy-flickery light vision. Went away after I instill Refresh tears eye drops. Neck stiffneck/achy:  mild headache all day. Took Ibuprofen 400mg tabs this am

Had visual alteration especially right eye this evening that lasted for a few minutes: seeing a wavy object, more pronounced on Right outer upper vision field. Relieved by Refresh Tears eye drops, also have mild tinnitus right ear, not so bothersome.
